She wiggled in his arms."Aww come on. I wanna play. I haven't played 
with anybot in forever." She then looked down at the ground far 
below them."YIPES!"  She covered her optics with her paws."Wh...Why 
are we so high up? I'm scared." She then thought of what he 
said."Others live? There are more of us here?" And what's 
korinthing? I'm not I'm not sick. I'm ok."  She started to 
cry."Mommy and Daddy didn't want me to get sick. So they sent me 
away."  She cried, "I want my Mommy!" she wailed out.
